16
00:01:04,333 --> 00:01:06,100
<c.Japanese>（比嘉）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>異状死には</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>間違いないんですけど</c.Japanese>

17
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:08,466
<c.Japanese>何か 不思議な死体で</c.Japanese>
