<c.Japanese>（石川）おう</c.Japanese>

22
00:01:14,466 --> 00:01:15,300
<c.Japanese>（立花）あとでな</c.Japanese>

23
00:01:18,733 --> 00:01:19,933
<c.Japanese>（市倉）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>だいぶ</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>仲良くなってきたな</c.Japanese>

24
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,933
<c.Japanese>（石川）そうすね</c.Japanese>

25
00:01:23,100 --> 00:01:24,100
<c.Japanese>（所轄の刑事）</c.Japanese>
