26
00:01:24,166 --> 00:01:25,000
<c.Japanese>（市倉）ご苦労さん</c.Japanese>

27
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:33,100
<c.Japanese>（所轄の刑事）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>死体が発見されたのは</c.Japanese>

28
00:01:33,433 --> 00:01:36,000
<c.Japanese>本日の</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>午前７時</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>45</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>分ごろです</c.Japanese>

29
00:01:36,066 --> 00:01:37,333
<c.Japanese>この家の主人が</c.Japanese>

30
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,333
<c.Japanese>昨夜午後</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>11</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>時ごろに</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>帰宅した際には</c.Japanese>

31
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,800
<c.Japanese>見当たらなかった</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>そうですので</c.Japanese>

32
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:42,900
<c.Japanese>その間にここで死んだか</c.Japanese>

33
00:01:42,966 --> 00:01:44,733
<c.Japanese>遺棄されたか</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>どちらかのはずです</c.Japanese>

34
00:01:45,033 --> 00:01:45,900
<c.Japanese>死亡推定時刻は</c.Japanese>

35
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,833
