<c.Japanese>３時までですので</c.Japanese>

36
00:01:47,900 --> 00:01:49,366
<c.Japanese>時間的にも合致します</c.Japanese>

37
00:01:49,666 --> 00:01:50,666
<c.Japanese>（市倉）身元は？</c.Japanese>

38
00:01:50,733 --> 00:01:51,800
<c.Japanese>（所轄の刑事）</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>分かっていません</c.Japanese>

39
00:01:51,933 --> 00:01:53,066
